Well, he shows up to the raid, and there are some people that don't like him expressing some stuff in different chat channels. Not really anything to worry about, because some people just hate some other people, ya know? The raid leader makes it know zone wide that Pidnus will not be on the raid. Pidnus then tells me saying that I NEED to get him into my group. I respond saying that I'm not in power, nor the leader of my group, sorry man. He responds saying he didn't run all the way to perma for nothing. I said that I understand and I will see what I can do, but I'm not promising anything. I wait for a little while whilst the rest of the stragglers show for the raid, and WOW do the rants start flowing about permafrost! Just from listening to them, there's no way I'm going to ruin the moral of a raid by trying to get some stranger-whos-name-rings-a-bell into my group, even if I could. After some shouting for a while, he shouts in the zone that I invited him and told him I was the raid leader blah blah blah.<br>
